Class Mksinterface_result

  • java.lang.Object
    • mksinterface.query.src.Mksinterface_result

  • public class Mksinterface_result
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which parses the response object which is given from the interface and provide all different items for the user Attention: This class do not check if the data is valid. If you add silly fields or other things be careful
    Author:
    ckaltenboeck
